snippet.title: Toy Pop (Arcade) - Gameplay
snippet.description: Oh man, NOSTALGIA!  I used to play this with my sister all the time~  Always loved the main stage theme; it's super catchy.  There are 44 boxes total, so this just shows 9/44ths of the game.  But I did show all the components of gameplay.  Every 8 boxes is a bonus stage, and the one before is a Wizard fight.  Box 44 is versus Mayjo, who seems to be sexist, cause she always aims for just Pino when Acha is there too.
